me_aurora-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>今天在日本首次与该歌曲的客座歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/aurora">AURORA</a>一起演奏了《Limousine》——请查看下面的片段。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="431" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/bring-me-the-horizon-oli-sykes-interview-post-human-nex-gen-3763537"><b>《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》关于“下一代”、乔丹·菲什之后的康复和生活：“你必须接受你是谁”</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌取自乐队最近的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/bring-me-the-horizon-post-human-nex-gen-review-3758948">Post Human: Nex Gen</a> 》，在千叶 ZOZO Marine Stadium 举行的 Summer Sonic Festival 上，观众有幸看到了乐队与这位挪威歌手一起首次表演这首歌。</p><p>在这里查看合作片段： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bring Me The Horizo​​n - 豪华轿车壮举。 AURORA (与 AURORA) - 日本演唱会 2024.08.18" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CNca2x4OPdc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在同一场演出中，谢菲尔德乐队还与日本金属乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/babymetal">BABYMETAL</a>合作推出了他们合作的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bring-me-the-horizon-and-babymetals-frantic-official-live-video-for-kingslayer-3558369">Kingslayer</a> ”版本。请看下面。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Bring Me The Horizo​​n - Kingslayer (feat. BABYMETAL) - 日本演唱会 2024.08.18" width="696" height="